sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Proxy as OAuth2 Proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant API as DS Pipelines API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant K8sAPI as OpenShift API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Pod as Pipeline Execution Pod
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Service<br/>8080/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant Storage as Minio/S3 Storage<br/>9000/443 TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL TLS
    participant PA as Persistence Agent<br/>8887/TCP gRPC

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission via UI

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS/443 - Unauthenticated
    Route->>OAuth: Redirect for authentication<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.3
    OAuth->>User: Return OAuth token<br/>User credentials validated
    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS/443 + Bearer Token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443 TLS1.2+<br/>Validate Bearer Token
    Proxy->>API: Forward to API server<br/>HTTP/8888 (trusted sidecar)
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL/3306 TLS<br/>Username/Password auth
    DB-->>API: Confirmation
    API->>WFC: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>Service Account Token
    API-->>Proxy: Pipeline created response
    Proxy-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON response

    Note over WFC,Storage: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution

    WFC->>K8sAPI: Create pipeline pods<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Service Account Token
    K8sAPI-->>Pod: Pod started
    Pod->>API: Report status<br/>gRPC/8887 mTLS (optional)<br/>SA Token auth
    Pod->>MLMD: Track artifact lineage<br/>gRPC/8080 mTLS<br/>SA Token auth
    MLMD->>DB: Store metadata<br/>MySQL/3306 TLS<br/>Username/Password
    Pod->>Storage: Upload/download artifacts<br/>HTTP or HTTPS/9000 or 443<br/>Access/Secret Keys
    Storage-->>Pod: Artifact data
    PA->>API: Query workflow state<br/>gRPC/8887 mTLS (optional)<br/>SA Token
    API-->>PA: Workflow status
    PA->>DB: Persist workflow state<br/>MySQL/3306 TLS<br/>Username/Password

    Note over User,DB: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    User->>Route: GET /metrics<br/>Prometheus scrape
    Route->>API: Forward metrics request<br/>HTTP/8080
    API-->>Route: Metrics data
    Route-->>User: Prometheus metrics
